        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Preventing PFAS Runoff at Airports Act</strong></p> <p>This bill temporarily allows the Federal Aviation Administration to cover 100% of the costs for airports to purchase and deploy equipment to test fire suppression systems that contain perfluoroalkyl and polyfluoroalkyl substances (PFAS) without discharging such substances. (PFAS are manmade substances and may have adverse human health effects.)</p> <p><br> </p>]]>
